---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout
  title="Charity & Community Support | Meon Valley Web"
  description="Meon Valley Web gives back to Hampshire communities with free charity websites and support for local causes. Learn about our community commitment."
  breadcrumbs={[
    { name: 'Home', href: '/' },
    { name: 'Charity & Community' },
  ]}
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-white via-primary-50/30 to-primary-100/50 py-20">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h1 class="text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">
          <span class="text-primary-500">Giving Back</span> to Our Community
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Our commitment to supporting worthwhile causes stems from personal experience 
          and a belief that helping others benefits our entire region.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Andrew's Story Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
        <!-- Content -->
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-black mb-8">
            A Personal Journey
          </h2>
          <div class="space-y-6 text-lg text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            <p>
              <strong class="text-black">Andrew</strong>, the founder of Meon Valley Web, has been creating websites 
              since Tim Berners-Lee said "Hi" - building digital solutions for companies like 
              <strong class="text-black">HSBC, Hoseasons, Eastern Electricity, French Country Cottages, and TravelBag</strong> 
              prior to 2007.
            </p>
            <p>
              But life changed dramatically in 2007 when Andrew's daughter Sophie was catastrophically 
              injured in a road traffic accident. During the <strong class="text-black">9 months she spent in a coma</strong> 
              and the <strong class="text-black">5 years in hospital</strong> that followed, Andrew spent countless hours 
              in hospital corridors and waiting rooms - time he used to keep his web development knowledge current.
            </p>
            <p>
              Sophie eventually came home to a purpose-built house in the beautiful Meon Valley, 
              where she lives with her family and animals. This experience opened Andrew's eyes 
              to the incredible work done by charities and the vital support they provide to families in crisis.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Image placeholder -->
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-2xl border border-gray-200 p-8">
            <div class="aspect-video rounded-xl relative overflow-hidden">
              <!-- Background image -->
              <img 
                src="/sophie-and-dad-canoeing.jpg" 
                alt="Sophie and dad canoeing" 
                class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover"
              />
              <!-- Overlay for better text readability -->
              <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/40 rounded-xl"></div>
              <!-- Text content in front -->
              <div class="relative z-10 flex items-center justify-center h-full">
                <div class="text-center text-white">
                  <svg class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z"></path>
                  </svg>
                  <p class="text-sm font-medium">Sophie's Story</p>
                  <p class="text-xs text-white/80">Inspiring our commitment to giving back</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Sophie's Gift Ball Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-black mb-6">
          Sophie's Gift Ball
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Turning personal tragedy into community benefit through fundraising and awareness.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
        <!-- Image placeholder -->
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-2xl border border-gray-200 p-8">
            <div class="aspect-video rounded-xl relative overflow-hidden">
              <!-- Background image -->
              <img 
                src="/ceretom-scanner.JPG" 
                alt="Ceretom CT scanner" 
                class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover"
              />
              <!-- Overlay for better text readability -->
              <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/40 rounded-xl"></div>
              <!-- Text content in front -->
              <div class="relative z-10 flex items-center justify-center h-full">
                <div class="text-center text-white">
                  <svg class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1"></path>
                  </svg>
                  <p class="text-sm font-medium">£300,000+ Raised</p>
                  <p class="text-xs text-white/80">For mobile CT scanner</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Content -->
        <div>
          <div class="space-y-6 text-lg text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            <p>
              The family started organising <strong class="text-black">Sophie's Gift Ball</strong>, an annual fundraising 
              event that has helped raise <strong class="text-black">over £300,000</strong> for a mobile CT scanner. 
              This vital piece of equipment helps people like Sophie while they're in ICU, providing 
              life-saving diagnostic capabilities directly at the bedside.
            </p>
            <p>
              Andrew & Alison also cycled the <strong class="text-black">South Downs Way</strong> and participated in numerous 
              other fundraising initiatives, always with the goal of giving back to the services 
              that supported their whole family during their darkest hours.
            </p>
            <p>
              The family has contributed to organisations including the <strong class="text-black">The Southampton University Hospitals Trust</strong>, the <strong class="text-black">Hampshire & Isle of Wight Air Ambulance</strong>, 
              the <strong class="text-black">QE2 Activity Centre</strong>, <strong class="text-black"> the Saints Disabled Supporters' Association</strong> and many other beneficial services that make 
              a real difference to people's lives.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Charity Websites Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-black mb-6">
          Websites We've Built for Charity
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Every quarter, we build a website for a charity free of charge. Here are some of the 
          organizations we've been proud to support.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
        <!-- SDSA -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-lg border border-gray-100 hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300">
          <div class="aspect-square rounded-xl relative overflow-hidden mb-6">
            <!-- Background image -->
            <img 
              src="/portfolio/sdsa.webp" 
              alt="SDSA website" 
              class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover"
            />
            <!-- Overlay to make background very faint -->
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-white/85 rounded-xl"></div>
            <!-- Logo and text content in front -->
            <div class="relative z-10 flex items-center justify-center h-full">
              <div class="text-center text-gray-800">
                <img 
                  src="/SDSA.webp" 
                  alt="SDSA logo" 
                  class="w-24 h-24 mx-auto mb-2 object-contain"
                />
                <p class="text-xs font-medium">SDSA</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-black mb-2">Saints Disabled Supporters' Association</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mb-4">
            Supporting disabled sports in Southampton. Sophie is a huge Southampton fan - don't judge!
          </p>
          <div class="text-xs text-primary-500 font-medium">Free Charity Website</div>
        </div>

        <!-- Wessex Whisky Club -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-lg border border-gray-100 hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300">
          <div class="aspect-square rounded-xl relative overflow-hidden mb-6">
            <!-- Background image -->
            <img 
              src="/portfolio/wessexwhiskyclub.webp" 
              alt="Wessex Whisky Club website" 
              class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover"
            />
            <!-- Overlay to make background very faint -->
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-white/85 rounded-xl"></div>
            <!-- Logo and text content in front -->
            <div class="relative z-10 flex items-center justify-center h-full">
              <div class="text-center text-gray-800">
                <img 
                  src="/wessex_whisky.webp" 
                  alt="Wessex Whisky logo" 
                  class="w-24 h-24 mx-auto mb-2 object-contain rounded-lg"
                />
                <p class="text-xs font-medium">Wessex Whisky</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-black mb-2">Wessex Whisky Club</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mb-4">
            A charity-benefiting club that brings whisky enthusiasts together for good causes.
          </p>
          <div class="text-xs text-primary-500 font-medium">Free Charity Website</div>
        </div>

        <!-- The Lace Guild -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-lg border border-gray-100 hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300">
          <div class="aspect-square rounded-xl relative overflow-hidden mb-6">
            <!-- Background image -->
            <img 
              src="/portfolio/thelaceguild.webp" 
              alt="The Lace Guild website" 
              class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover"
            />
            <!-- Overlay to make background very faint -->
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-white/85 rounded-xl"></div>
            <!-- Icon and text content in front -->
            <div class="relative z-10 flex items-center justify-center h-full">
              <div class="text-center text-gray-800">
                <svg class="w-20 h-20 mx-auto mb-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M7 21a4 4 0 01-4-4V5a2 2 0 012-2h4a2 2 0 012 2v12a4 4 0 01-4 4zM21 5a2 2 0 00-2-2h-4a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a4 4 0 004 4 4 4 0 004-4V5z"></path>
                </svg>
                <p class="text-xs font-medium">Lace Guild</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-black mb-2">The Lace Guild</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mb-4">
            Preserving the traditional craft of lace-making and supporting artisans.
          </p>
          <div class="text-xs text-primary-500 font-medium">Free Charity Website</div>
        </div>

        <!-- Two Dogs and an Awning -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-lg border border-gray-100 hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300">
          <div class="aspect-square rounded-xl relative overflow-hidden mb-6">
            <!-- Background image -->
            <img 
              src="/portfolio/twodogsananawning.webp" 
              alt="Two Dogs and an Awning website" 
              class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover"
            />
            <!-- Overlay to make background very faint -->
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-white/85 rounded-xl"></div>
            <!-- Logo and text content in front -->
            <div class="relative z-10 flex items-center justify-center h-full">
              <div class="text-center text-gray-800">
                <img 
                  src="/twodogs.webp" 
                  alt="Two Dogs logo" 
                  class="w-24 h-24 mx-auto mb-2 object-contain"
                />
                <p class="text-xs font-medium">Two Dogs</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-black mb-2">Two Dogs and an Awning</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mb-4">
            Personal friends who've raised thousands for the Trussell Trust food bank network.
          </p>
          <div class="text-xs text-primary-500 font-medium">Free Charity Website</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Our Philosophy Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-primary-500 relative overflow-hidden">
    <!-- Background decorative elements -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0">
      <div class="absolute top-20 right-20 w-72 h-72 bg-white/10 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
      <div class="absolute bottom-20 left-20 w-96 h-96 bg-white/5 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="relative z-10 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-8">
        Why We Give Back
      </h2>
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <p class="text-xl text-primary-100 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
          We believe that helping worthwhile causes benefits the region as a whole - and thus us. 
          When our community thrives, we all thrive together.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-primary-100 leading-relaxed">
          Every charity website we build, every pound we donate, and every hour we volunteer 
          creates a ripple effect of positive change throughout Hampshire and beyond. 
          It's not just about giving back - it's about building a stronger, more connected community.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- How We Help Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-black mb-6">
          How We Support Charities
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Our commitment goes beyond just building websites - we provide comprehensive 
          digital support to help charities achieve their goals.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="text-center p-6">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary-100 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-primary-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 20l4-16m4 4l4 4-4 4M6 16l-4-4 4-4"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-black mb-4">Free Website Development</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            Complete website design and development at no cost, including mobile-responsive 
            design and SEO optimization.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center p-6">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary-100 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-primary-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 12h14M5 12a2 2 0 01-2-2V6a2 2 0 012-2h14a2 2 0 012 2v4a2 2 0 01-2 2M5 12a2 2 0 00-2 2v4a2 2 0 002 2h14a2 2 0 002-2v-4a2 2 0 00-2-2m-2-4h.01M17 16h.01"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-black mb-4">Discounted Hosting</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            Reliable, fast hosting at significantly reduced rates to help charities 
            keep their ongoing costs low.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center p-6">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary-100 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-primary-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M18.364 5.636l-3.536 3.536m0 5.656l3.536 3.536M9.172 9.172L5.636 5.636m3.536 9.192L5.636 18.364M12 12h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-black mb-4">Ongoing Support</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            Continued technical support and maintenance to ensure charity websites 
            stay secure and up-to-date.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-black mb-6">
        Know a Charity That Needs Help?
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-8 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        If you know a worthwhile charity that could benefit from a professional website, 
        we'd love to hear from you. Let's work together to make a difference.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a href="/contact" class="bg-primary-500 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg hover:bg-primary-600 transition-colors duration-200 font-medium text-lg">
          Nominate a Charity
        </a>
        <a href="/portfolio" class="border-2 border-gray-300 text-gray-700 px-8 py-4 rounded-lg hover:border-primary-500 hover:text-primary-500 transition-colors duration-200 font-medium text-lg">
          View Our Work
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</MainLayout>